query:
SELECT tn.name as namespace_name, nt.name, nt.version
            FROM tasker.tasks t
            JOIN tasker.named_tasks nt ON t.named_task_uuid = nt.named_task_uuid
            JOIN tasker.task_namespaces tn ON nt.task_namespace_uuid = tn.task_namespace_uuid
            WHERE t.task_uuid = $1
